Class Linker

java.lang.Object
  linker.Linker
Direct Known Subclasses:
BugzillaLinker, EmailLinker, JiraLinker
public abstract class Linker
extends java.lang.Object

Abstract implementation of the Linker, Extending classes should override the Link() method to define their own methods of linking to Commit

LinkFromIssueThreadItems

public void LinkFromIssueThreadItems()

Links Item to Issue by parsing the date of the item
and the date of commits linked to the Item's thread. Then after finding a 'correct'
commit, the item->commit link get's placed in the TechnicalDb. This algorithm
is only performed on the items that are children of threads.
